title: Trials and Confessions of a Housekeeper
creator: T. S. Arthur
description: LibriVox recording of Trials and Confessions of a Housekeeper, by T. S. Arthur. Read by Kehinde. Is housekeeping such a trial? Mrs. Smith thinks so and confesses all in this merry account of her escapades and near disasters! (Summary by Kehinde) For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B format available
